    "In Thailand, e-commerce platforms currently employ artificial intelligence (AI) algorithms to provide personalized product recommendations to users, leveraging their browsing and purchase histories (Kasemsap, 2023).",
    "This implementation aims to improve the entire shopping experience for customers.",
